L - R Mr. Paschal Samu , Zonal Coordinator Special Control Unit Against Money Laundering (SCUML) of the EFCC Lagos , Mrs. Taiwo Ganiyat Olusesi , Registrar CEO Institute of Chartered Secretaries and Administrators of Nigeria (ICSAN) Mr. Daniel Isei ,Director (SCUML EFCC ) Mr. Taiwo ' Gbenga Owokolade President ICSAN & Mr. Francis Olawale , Honourary Treasurer ICSAN during a courtesy visit by the senior officials of the EFCC to ICSAN in Lagos recently

        
 

